From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Thu, 5 Feb 2026 23:40:51 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: cix: Thermal zone improvements

- Rename thermal zones to tz-* pattern for clarity and <20 char limit
- Add switch_on trip point (60C) to prevent IPA governor from
  always being in passive state with single trip point zones
- Update GPU power model thermal-zone reference to match
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6.dts  |  8 +--
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts |  8 +--
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1.dtsi          | 67 ++++++++++++++++++----
 3 files changed, 64 insertions(+), 19 deletions(-)

